    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously preserved and maintained since new. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car comes with a complete, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
